1
00:00:00,210 --> 00:00:03,380
Handsome, yet fragile.
Beautiful, but timid.

2
00:00:03,460 --> 00:00:07,210
You act tough to hide
your vulnerable side.

3
00:00:08,960 --> 00:00:09,960
I'm okay.

4
00:00:11,250 --> 00:00:12,250
Thank you.

5
00:00:14,420 --> 00:00:15,580
There's something inside.

6
00:00:17,670 --> 00:00:19,040
You gave me a snack last time.

7
00:00:20,250 --> 00:00:21,250
This is a little something in return.

8
00:00:23,210 --> 00:00:24,210
For me?

9
00:00:25,080 --> 00:00:27,540
If you just give me
the same thing back,

10
00:00:28,130 --> 00:00:29,790
it kind of defeats the purpose
of my gift, don't you think?

11
00:00:29,880 --> 00:00:30,960
If you don't want it, forget it.

12
00:00:30,960 --> 00:00:32,420
Too bad, I'm keeping it.
No take-backs.

13
00:00:32,670 --> 00:00:33,670
Okay.

14
00:00:34,000 --> 00:00:35,330
From the one I got...

15
00:00:35,500 --> 00:00:36,790
I got this!

16
00:00:36,960 --> 00:00:37,960
A ring!

17
00:00:38,080 --> 00:00:39,540
Nice!

18
00:00:40,130 --> 00:00:41,710
I wonder if I'll get it in this one.

19
00:00:41,710 --> 00:00:42,830
It's the secret one.

20
00:00:42,830 --> 00:00:44,790
There's no way you'd get it that easily.

21
00:00:44,790 --> 00:00:45,880
I got it!

22
00:00:52,670 --> 00:00:55,420
Such long, beautiful eyelashes.

23
00:00:55,630 --> 00:00:59,290
You were just thinking about
how long my eyelashes are, weren't you?

24
00:00:59,290 --> 00:01:01,460
When you start to fall for someone,

25
00:01:01,460 --> 00:01:03,290
you notice things like the length of their eyelashes.

26
00:01:12,500 --> 00:01:13,210
I'm sorry.

27
00:01:13,500 --> 00:01:15,670
I just couldn't help myself.

28
00:01:16,080 --> 00:01:17,330
Don't stop.

29
00:01:18,750 --> 00:01:20,540
You're so cute.

30
00:01:20,540 --> 00:01:21,750
Honestly...

31
00:01:26,750 --> 00:01:27,710
Iijima-san.

32
00:01:27,750 --> 00:01:30,420
The police would like a word with you.

33
00:01:30,500 --> 00:01:31,540
Huh?

34
00:01:32,000 --> 00:01:34,670
For goodness' sake...
Didn't I tell you to stay put?
